{"tid":1065350,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"搭開泰航嘅您可唔可以入一入黎唔該","createTime":"2019-03-17T07:39:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T10:45:25.000Z","uid":38832,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a6f0a22306babf519fcf637cca8e7683c9c2434c","tid":1065350,"uid":38832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小弟最近拜託朋友幫手<span style=\"color: violet;\"><a href=\"http://CheapTickets.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FCheapTickets.hk&d=vfAPSPM9tzlrjOAF5hGH%2F1znTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=2c3564e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">CheapTickets.hk</a></span>度買咗兩張來回香港同曼谷嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">泰國航空</span></span>機票，因為平時自己買開都冇乜特別所以就冇留意啲細則。<br />\n就係今日，我收到email可以揀位乜乜77，然後揀完就收到個email，然後我就見到啲咁嘅嘢......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xa6nC4D.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXa6nC4D.png&h=bd25a506&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家就頭痕緊個friend唔係同行人，但個email又講到一定要有佢係度先上到機，佢究竟會唔會一定check呢？我叫個friend寫張授權書同影印啲卡資料俾我又得唔得呢？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">各位搭開嘅巴打絲打我有冇咩方法解決到呢？</span>"},{"pid":"87af38a44efdda36f3d61841da8c43c6c4565f88","tid":1065350,"uid":37876,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:42:04.000Z","msg":"點解你唔打去航空公司問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a69505bc9223903cacc3b66df9a2ed3a890e63e","tid":1065350,"uid":176780,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:44:06.000Z","msg":"聯絡客戶支援 下面有email<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f912327b72958aa83b90cd37abd7e09ebce